Could i use tailscale or vercel instead of ngrok?
Yes, you can use Tailscale instead of ngrok, and it is actually the preferred method for most users because it is more secure and creates a permanent private connection. Vercel, however, is not a direct replacement for ngrok in this workflow and serves a completely different purpose. 
