Tailscale: The "Private Tunnel" (Recommended)
Tailscale creates a secure "Mesh VPN" between your devices. Once installed on both your remote Mucho3D server and your local Blender machine, they act as if they are on the same Wi-Fi. 
Medium
Medium
 +1
Persistent IP: Unlike ngrok, which often gives you a new URL every time it restarts, Tailscale gives your server a stable IP address (e.g., 100.x.y.z) that never changes. 
